
To configure:

Create a file called ~/.azclientrc with the following:

URI https://server.domain.tld/artaxerxes
PROXY https://user:password@server.domain.tld/cgi-bin/artaxerxes.cgi

where:

server.domain.tld = the remote server where Artaxerxes is available
user = user for HTTP authentication to access the service
password = corresponding password

